Name: Snooker-online multiplayer snooker game!
About the game: World best online multiplayer snooker game! Features: Snooker, 8 ball pool and 9 ball pool all in one. NEWBIE TRAINING Training courses for newbie. Learn snooker skills and operations. 1-ON-1 RANDOM MATCH Random play with world wide snooker players. ARENA of Professional, Master and Hardcore Higher coin and experience point reward. PLAY WITH FRIEND CUES AND TABLES Rich cues and tables you can select. LEVEL UP Level up with your wins. LEADERBOARD World wide ranking of players winning. INGAME CHAT Voice chat with player from anywhere in game. ACHIEVEMENTS Reach achievement to get rewards.
